\cs16\fs16\super $} Contents for O'NO 99 Help}} Contents for O'NO 99 Help
\par \pard\plain \s17\sa120 \f7\fs20\lang3081 The object of the game is to avoid totaling 99 points or more -- the total number of points that would cause you to lose that round of play.
\par To learn how to use Help, press {\fs18 F1}.
\par \pard \s17\sb240\sa60 {\b The Game
